des: "This recipe was given to me by my Mother, who was a wonderful cook. Everything she made was to perfection. I just know that everyone who tries this will love its unique flavor. Serve with cut vegetable tray."
ins: Blend mayonnaise, tuna, anchovy fillets, onion, celery, potatoes, green onion, black olives, garlic, Worcestershire sauce, salt, and hot pepper sauce in a blender until completely smooth; transfer to a bowl, cover with plastic wrap, and refrigerate until chilled, at least 1 hour.
